t: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tweet link .https://twitter.com/JennyBwood/status/1532398022784692225</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/n8xAJsQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mech0T1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>hero from Alaska removes possum from NYC bar</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/I28ktqK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CwMB63G.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/I28ktqK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[poponthebeezer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Politicians &amp; Bad Policy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KJY7qTf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2Otu9f8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KJY7qTf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oh my god it's perfect</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MOOV1J5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ywuktti.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9JHS32Q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sauce:
https://twitter.com/Pandamoanimum/status/1526503971719888898</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MOOV1J5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MizWeirdo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>2nd time in 2 weeks I found a scared kitten in the middle of the highway</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/p9SVyHh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fQ79bMp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I found this one in the middle of the interstate. He was so far in the roadway that my only option was to straddle him with my car to avoid hitting him. He was cowered in a puddle of what I assume was his own urine from fear. Poor thing can't keep its eyes open. Wouldn't stop trembling. Has an injury to its nose and mouth to be evaluated by a vet.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cfbemUY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I was on a 4 hour drive when I found it (I think it's a him, but haven't gotten close enough to say for sure). His mouth is a little swollen but eyes and pupils are reactive. Was given water and a small amount of wet food.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UMfnI9I.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Small amount of blood on his face. But his spirit is improving. Send good vibes for this little guy! We have a vet appointment later</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EH68q0f.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Melodie, the first kitten I found in the middle of a local highway during rush hour. This is her shortly after I rescued her. She was uninjured when I found her and was given a clean bill of health. She is so sweet and playful. As soon as I found the other kitten on our trip, she immediately started taking care of him. What a sweetheart!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6daUnQJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She is doing great and is happily integrated into my family.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/p9SVyHh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[literalcatlady]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>360 degree camera in the mouth. PT.2</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LI6fYAB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4s8BjDX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You can see part 1 in my timeline</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LI6fYAB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WakeUp2Yourself]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thoughts and prayers anyone?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cBcXXj8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3TjA6S2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LiYAORN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6Km537e.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cBcXXj8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It got serious really quickly</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CQFK4Az</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QV2tv9X.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CQFK4Az</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BryansArt]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Like the 18 year olds</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6YYlXHc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9lRDQIj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6YYlXHc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I am Iron Man</ti